### Islamic Finance & Zakat Management Manual Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/api

### 1. Calculate Zakat for a Household
POST {{baseUrl}}/islamic-finance/zakat/calculate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "householdId": "household-123",
  "calculationDate": "2024-01-01",
  "assetTypes": ["CASH", "SAVINGS", "INVESTMENT"]
}

### 2. Get Zakat Calculations History
GET {{baseUrl}}/islamic-finance/zakat/calculations/household-123?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 3. Get Latest Zakat Calculation
GET {{baseUrl}}/islamic-finance/zakat/calculations/household-123/latest
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 4. Record Zakat Payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/islamic-finance/zakat/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "householdId": "household-123",
  "amount": 2500000,
  "currency": "IDR",
  "paymentDate": "2024-01-15",
  "hijriDate": "5/7/1445 AH",
  "transactionId": "transaction-456",
  "notes": "Annual zakat payment for 1445 AH"
}

### 5. Get Zakat Payment History
GET {{baseUrl}}/islamic-finance/zakat/payments/household-123
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 6. Create Zakat Reminder
POST {{baseUrl}}/islamic-finance/zakat/reminders
