GET {{baseUrl}}/islamic-finance/zakat/reminders/household-123?activeOnly=true
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 8. Get Upcoming Zakat Reminders
GET {{baseUrl}}/islamic-finance/zakat/reminders/household-123/upcoming?daysAhead=30
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

