### Variables for testing
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@authToken = your-jwt-token-here

### Test Data Setup
### Before running these tests, ensure you have:
### 1. A valid household with ID "household-123"
### 2. Some accounts associated with the household
### 3. Valid authentication token
### 4. Database is running and migrated

### Expected Responses:
### - Zakat calculations should return proper calculation results
### - Compliance updates should reflect in subsequent queries
### - Reports should contain comprehensive Islamic finance data
### - Dashboard should provide overview of all Islamic finance features
